name: Cindy Milley Tom
description: I am a very warm and friendly person with a good sense of humor and passionate . I give freely of myself and i am always ready to lend a hand to someone who truely love..I am strong and independent and no matter how bad things get i am always looking for that silver lining. I still believe in true love and I believe that life is magical and i don’t sweat the small stuff. I’m very spontaneous and adventurous and I love the outdoors. I believe strongly in family and celebrating tradition.
